{"tid":752844,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"別高興 別以為叫高普","createTime":"2018-07-23T06:42:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T10:01:39.000Z","uid":38189,"like":210,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"e46b0a790f977aff5b34b2d24acbee7c31ea0e2f","tid":752844,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:42:12.000Z","msg":"臨完場 輸波都只怪膠猁乏勁 <br />\n整定 球員醜態現形 <br />\n<br />\n誰嫌頹 敗局亦不易平定 <br />\n遑論領先 鏝城~ <br />\n<br />\n別高興 別以為靠高普 <br />\n萬季千季都會依猁意願來留步 <br />\n下一季 前四仍會不保 <br />\n若要賭 光臨當舖 <br />\n<br />\n誰贏誰 英超不需買兵便命定 <br />\n他年 輪迴今季劇情 <br />\n誰亡誰 猁在歷史下效命 <br />\n如犯錯般受刑<br />\n<br />\n別高興 別以為靠高普 <br />\n來季今季都會依猁意願來停步 <br />\n下一季 前四仍會不保 <br />\n若再賭 輸埋隻撈 <br />\n<br />\n別失敬 別以為要聲討 <br />\n上季失冠都是依猁意願來營造 <br />\n在今季 回顧誰教得好 <br />\n若要數 渣士最高"},{"pid":"85b8a1ef1eb0a973595e91138b068e7a5d23084e","tid":752844,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:42:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"734f87f5678f29483d0c0cfde2001dfacb5a2922","tid":752844,"uid":2033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:43:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3bd1506410e5e69d946e099a2cd5e8569493dbc","tid":752844,"uid":14812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:46:10.000Z","msg":"羅帥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"555bfd274aac31d57d03f564967aa40a09e4b462","tid":752844,"uid":18543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:46:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87b87c35ba17f57f8ca47a9fa85f21cbc3f9ea53","tid":752844,"uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T06:46:49.000Z","msg":"熱狗果然有才華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />